Miquelon is covered under Creative Common License Attribution Share-Alike (CC BY-SA). In another word, the source code is in the open source.

The brief summary of Creative Common License Attribution Share-Alike:

- You are free to copy, share and distribute the work.
- You are free to remix the work, even for commercial purposes. However, you must credit the authour of the source code.
- If you alter the source code, you can only distribut the altered work with this license or a similar license.

The full information of the license is available here: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/
